{"tid":1614921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比政府冷處理核彈事件","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:05:24.000Z","uid":68493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"304c7a9578877c43185a096c97c7a82be3ef1fb0","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"打爛鋪頭既事一定會比傳媒大肆報導<br />\n雖然民意已經歸邊，大家點都唔會割，但更重要係唔好比政府有機會shift focus 去呢件事上<br />\n更加唔好加重文宣負擔<br />\n我地要做係大力去令全世界關注開槍事件<br />\n另外，繼續爆野就會比機會黑社會做野，到時偷野等等就會屈落我地身上<br />\n所以大家要冷靜，萬事小心處理"},{"pid":"8a27c84ae92d502235be8472df99b4848de7a692","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0358bc45cd3481f8e348e7d4d09ba949e03ed41","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f08f7d3ae6ec90d901fbc10d7161039a891dc8f","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"da093c68ab749b71fa5de4c7965ae0df9c3e89cc","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"推完"},{"pid":"cf35d2eb88b663551a22ea7e2a7b3798b7a62a37","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"大家好"},{"pid":"57c8ee2266d4e79dc1038a2f6e9697231f18cb5e","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"我真心的"},{"pid":"873a07da84c5ad3a6b1d65df5a7ff2c2a4e2fa0b","tid":1614921,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf76ddc19f4911c56c35057aa63fbadb7b345de8","tid":1614921,"uid":34996,"like":0,"